llenge Tour because success at this level soon leads to promotion to the [[European Tour]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Dates!!Tournament!!Host country!!Winner!![[Official World Golf Ranking|OWGR]]<br>points!!Purse (\u20ac)!!Notes\n|-\n| 2 Feb || [[Limpopo Championship]] || [[South Africa]] || {{flagicon|ZAF}} [[J. C. Ritchie]] (1) || align=center|13 || align=right|$250,000 || Co-sanctioned with the [[Sunshine Tour]]\n|-\n| 9 Feb || [[RAM Cape Town Open]] || [[South Africa]] || {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Anton Karlsson (golfer)|Anton Karlsson]] (1) || align=center|13 || align=right|$250,000 || Co-sanctioned with the [[Sunshine Tour]]\n|-\n| 16 Feb || [[Dimension Data Pro-Am]] || [[South Africa]] || {{flagicon|ZAF}} [[Christiaan Bezuidenhout]] (n/a) || align=center|13 || align=right|$340,000 || Co-sanctioned with the [[Sunshine Tour]]\n|-\n| <s>10 May</s> || [[Prague Golf Challenge]] || [[Czech Republic]] || ''Cancelled''{{efn|name=cancelcovid}} || align=center| || align=right|205,000 || \n|-\n| <s>7 Jun</s> || [[D+D Real Czech Challenge]] || [[Czech Republic]] || ''Cancelled''{{efn|name=cancelcovid}} || align=center| || align=right|205,000 || \n|-\n| TBC<br/><s>14 Jun</s> || [[Match Play 9]] || [[Spain]] || ''Postponed''{{efn|name=postponecovid|Postponed due to [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.europeantour.com/challenge-tour/news/articles/detail/statement-on-the-challenge-de-espana/ |title=Statement on the Challenge de Espa\u00f1a |website=PGA European Tour |date=18 March 2020 |accessdate=21 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=apr17upd/>}} || align=center|12 || align=right|200,000 || \n|-\n| TBC<br/><s>5 Jul</s><br/><s>17 May</s> || [[Challenge de Espa\u00f1a]] || [[Spain]] || ''Postponed''{{efn|name=postponecovid}} || align=center|12 || align=right|200,000 || \n|-\n| <s>5 Jul</s> || [[D+D Real Slovakia Challenge]] || [[Slovakia]] || ''Cancelled''{{efn|name=cancelcovid}} || align=center| || align=right|205,000 || \n|-\n|